strings.Value: "Now I am the lawful ruler of these lands."
"I hope you haven't been attacking the neighboring villages and settlements..."
[Attack] "I've changed my mind. I have no wish to see mites on my lands!"
"You asked me to deal with Chief Sootscale, Queen. He is defeated."
"You now ruler? Sweet! If have many children, send one. I catch one of mine and we make marriage dynasty!"
"I bored with no kobold," {n}sighs the Queen sadly.{/n} "Was such fun war! Fight, carnage, prisoner torture. Sweet!"
"Very bored with no war! I invite kobold feast, gut many squirrel and hare, but they no eat and no fun. Ugh, silly kobold. Why we mercy them?"
"I order build new Sacred Hall for new relic. Gather much bug waste to decorate!"
"We honor alliance, no attack. We only scare one fool, who catch fish. They run and scream so fun! But we no even kill him, no-no." {n}The Queen squints cunningly.{/n}
"I know this talk peace be joke. And silly kobold believe? Poor silly kobold."
"Ha-ha, get old kobold hide? Sweet! Take reward."
"You grow bored with no war? I can help you with that!"
"War with you? No, no! We happy bored!"
